{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_01_02",
  "title": "miho 2話 いつか返り咲く",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――生放送当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of live broadcasting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "大変ご無沙汰してます\nお声を掛けていただいて、本当にありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while.\nThank you so much for reaching out to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、リハの準備は出来てます\nそれで、音響について少し確認いただきたいことが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ I'm ready for the rehearsal.\nAlso‚ there's something I'd like to confirm about the sound.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。分かりました\nfranとkanaにもそう伝えておきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ understood.\nI'll convey that to fran and kana as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 2333.3333333000005,
          "startTime": 20.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "これ、つまらない物ですけど\nよろしければみなさんでお召し上がり下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is nothing special‚\nbut if you'd like‚ please have some.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ、{user}さん\n今日のステージが終わった後、時間はありますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ {user}-san.\nAfter today's stage‚ do you have some free time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフさんで打ち上げをするそうなので\n貴方も参加させてほしいと頼んでおきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're planning a staff gathering‚\nand they asked if you could join too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "この番組のプロデューサーも来るそうなので\n顔を繋いでおけば、後々も役に立つと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The producer of this show is also going to be there.\nIf you can make a connection‚ it might be useful in the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はは……ありがとうございます\nいやもう、どっちがマネージャーなんだか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… Thank you.\nI mean‚ which one of us is the manager anyway…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "今日はファンのみなさんと久々にお会い出来て\n嬉しくて……でも、それ以上にほっとした、かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ being able to meet the fans after a long time…\nIt makes me happy‚ but more than that‚ I feel relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "私達、いろいろありましたから……でも、ええ\nここがスリクスのホームグラウンドなんだなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've been through a lot…\nBut‚ yes‚ this is IIIX's home ground‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3333.33333329999,
          "startTime": 71.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（……圧巻のステージだな）\n（さすが、元BIG4のスリクス）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Impressive stage.）\n（As expected from the former BIG4‚ IIIX.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（彼女達だけで、ここまで立派にこなせるなら）\n（これは本当に、俺の出番はないなあ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If they can handle it this well on their own…）\n（I truly have no role here…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4900.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 85
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい\n……相談があるんです、少しお時間いただけませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry.\n…I have something to discuss. Could you spare some time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん？　どうしました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "miho-san? What's the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2299.9999999999973,
          "startTime": 94.2
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2699.9999999999886,
          "startTime": 94.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "さっき昔の知り合いに連絡して、今度東京で開催される\nアイドルイベントについて尋ねてみたのですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I contacted an old acquaintance earlier and\nasked about an idol event that will be held in Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.0893468633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 106.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "イベント出演には前向きなお返事をいただけたんです\n……ただ、後から条件を付けられまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I received a positive response regarding our participation in the event…\n…However‚ later on‚ they added a condition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "私達だけではなくて、星見プロにいる他の……\nサニーピースやリズノワにも出てもらえないかと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just for us‚ but also for the other members of Hoshimi Pro‚\nlike Sunny Peace and LizNoir‚ they want them to participate as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 119.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達も出るなら\nスリクスを出演させてもいいというお話でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If they agree to participate…\n…we are allowed to have IIIX perform in the event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "要するに、バーター取引ということです\n芸能界では、別にめずらしいことでもないでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In other words‚ it's a barter trade.\nIn the entertainment industry‚ it's not particularly rare‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "確かにめずらしいことじゃありませんけど\nそれは、新人を売り出す場合なんかでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ it's not rare.\nBut isn't that something done when promoting newcomers?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 136.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスみたいな、人気も実力もあるグループが\nそんな扱いをされるとは聞いたことがありませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've never heard of a group like IIIX‚\nwith both popularity and talent‚ being treated that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2021179199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 143.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_02-mhk016.m4a",
